      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TAKEOVER TARGET (8) rises out to this distance for the first time. Missed the frame last time when 4th and beaten 5.5 lengths (22.40) at this track. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. HE PLAYED ONE (1) held his own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only 1.5 lengths (29.15) behind Honey Bunny at this track. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Will give a great sight again. BARNSLEY (2) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Federal Tommy (28.98) in a Grade 5/6. Must be included in calculations. ROSE BELLE (6) was well fancied last time on the strength of a win two back but could only manage fifth (29.85) at this track.",
